ing: 1 (15 ounce) can garbanzo beans, drained with liquid reserved
n: Healthy Halloween Roasted Red Pepper Hummus
des: "The red pepper gives this hummus a lovely orange color, perfect for Halloween. Serve with black corn chips."
ins: Combine garbanzo beans, lemon juice, olive oil, tahini, red pepper, salt, and garlic in a food processor; blend until smooth. Stir in reserved liquid to desired texture.
